  <div class="container">
    <h3 class="font-weight-medium p-heads pt-5">SpeekIO solution makes hiring process for HR managers easier, faster and more detailed, making it the ultimate hiring experience. Hiring managers can create a job advertisement and can also create initial screening exam test. This cloud based solution can be accessed and can be used from anywhere in the world. I led the ideation, strategy and design for its web based solution.</h3>
