        <div class="col-md-6"><small class="text-muted">SURVEY FINDINGS</small>
          <h3 class="font-weight-bold p-heads">“Creating online exam test and filtering best candidate through ranking system topped the list of hiring process”</h3>
          <p>A sample of the different set of questions asked from the participants is shared. Items with the highest opportunity are highlighted in blue.</p>
